## 2. Redux Architecture

මේ project එකේ **Redux Toolkit (RTK)** + **RTK Query** use කරනවා. Parts 3 කට divide කරන්න පුලුවන්:

```
Redux
├── State Slices (features/)   → Local global state (auth, UI)
├── RTK Query (services/)      → Server state, API calls, caching
└── Store (app/store.ts)       → ඔක්කොම bind කරන central store
```

---

## 3. Redux Store — [src/app/store.ts](file:///c:/Users/shanu/Desktop/Project%20Git/mabarana-group-admin-dashboard/src/app/store.ts)

```ts
export const store = configureStore({
  reducer: {
    meta: metaSlice.reducer,   // UI state
    auth: authSlice.reducer,   // Auth state
    [apiSlice.reducerPath]: apiSlice.reducer, // RTK Query cache
  },
  middleware(getDefaultMiddleware) {
    return getDefaultMiddleware().concat(apiSlice.middleware); // RTK Query middleware
  },
  devTools: true,
});

export type RootState = ReturnType<typeof store.getState>;
export type AppDispatch = typeof store.dispatch;
```

| Reducer key | Source | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `meta` | `features/metaSlice` | Left sidebar open/close state |
| [auth](file:///c:/Users/shanu/Desktop/Project%20Git/mabarana-group-admin-dashboard/src/services/apiSlice.ts#39-110) | `features/authSlice` | User info + JWT tokens |
| `api` | `services/apiSlice` | RTK Query cache + API state |

