## 4. Feature Slices (Local State)

### 4.1 `authSlice` — [src/features/authSlice.ts](file:///c:/Users/shanu/Desktop/Project%20Git/mabarana-group-admin-dashboard/src/features/authSlice.ts)

Authentication state manage කරන slice. **Redux + localStorage** sync කරනවා.

**Initial State:**
```ts
{
  userInfo: JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("user")),
  selectedBranch: JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("selectedBranch")),
  accessToken: localStorage.getItem("accessToken"),
  refreshToken: localStorage.getItem("refreshToken"),
}
```

**Actions (Reducers):**

| Action | Description |
|---|---|
| [setUserInfo(payload)](file:///c:/Users/shanu/Desktop/Project%20Git/mabarana-group-admin-dashboard/src/features/authSlice.ts#30-34) | User info set කරනවා + localStorage update |
| [setTokens({ accessToken, refreshToken })](file:///c:/Users/shanu/Desktop/Project%20Git/mabarana-group-admin-dashboard/src/features/authSlice.ts#44-50) | JWT tokens update + localStorage |
| [setBranchInfo(payload)](file:///c:/Users/shanu/Desktop/Project%20Git/mabarana-group-admin-dashboard/src/features/authSlice.ts#50-54) | Selected branch save කරනවා + localStorage |
| [logout()](file:///c:/Users/shanu/Desktop/Project%20Git/mabarana-group-admin-dashboard/src/features/authSlice.ts#34-44) | State + localStorage clear කරනවා |
| [logoutBranch()](file:///c:/Users/shanu/Desktop/Project%20Git/mabarana-group-admin-dashboard/src/features/authSlice.ts#54-58) | Branch selection clear කරනවා |

**Usage example:**
```tsx
import { useDispatch, useSelector } from "react-redux";
import { logout, setUserInfo } from "@/features/authSlice";
import type { RootState } from "@/app/store";

const dispatch = useDispatch();
const userInfo = useSelector((state: RootState) => state.auth.userInfo);

dispatch(setUserInfo({ name: "John", role: "admin" }));
dispatch(logout());
```

