## 5. RTK Query — API Layer

### 5.1 `apiSlice` — [src/services/apiSlice.ts](file:///c:/Users/shanu/Desktop/Project%20Git/mabarana-group-admin-dashboard/src/services/apiSlice.ts)

**Base API** slice — සියලුම service slices මේකෙන් `injectEndpoints` කරනවා.

#### 🔑 Key Features:

**1. Automatic Token Refresh (Mutex-protected)**

Access token expire (401) වුණාම automatically refresh token use කරලා retry කරනවා. Concurrent requests handle කරන්න `async-mutex` use කරනවා.

```
Request → 401 TOKEN_EXPIRED
       → Mutex acquire (prevent parallel refreshes)
       → POST /users/refresh-token (with refreshToken)
       → New tokens save (Redux + localStorage)
       → Original request retry
       → Mutex release
```

**2. Tag Types (Cache Invalidation)**
```ts
tagTypes: [
  "Auth", "Merchants", "Branches", "Users",
  "Organizations", "Subscriptions", "Banners",
  "Customers", "Discounts", "Notifications", "Metrics"
]
```
> Tag type use කරලා endpoint data invalidate/refetch කරන්න පුලුවන්. E.g., merchant add කළාට පස්සේ `"Merchants"` tag invalidate කරනවා.

**3. Two Base Queries**

| Query | Token Used | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| [baseQuery](file:///c:/Users/shanu/Desktop/Project%20Git/mabarana-group-admin-dashboard/src/services/apiSlice.ts#39-110) | `accessToken` | Normal API calls |
| `baseQueryWithToken` | `refreshToken` | Token refresh endpoint only |

---

### 5.2 Service Slices — `src/services/`

සියලුම service slices `apiSlice.injectEndpoints()` use කරලා endpoints add කරනවා.

| File | Tag | Key Endpoints |
|---|---|---|
| `authSlice.ts` | `Auth` | login, logout, refreshToken |
| `merchantSlice.ts` | `Merchants` | getMerchants, addMerchant, editMerchant |
| `branchSlice.ts` | `Branches` | getBranches, addBranch, editBranch |
| `userSlice.ts` | `Users` | getUsers, addUser, editUser |
| `organizationSlice.ts` | `Organizations` | getOrganizations, addOrg |
| `subscriptionSlice.ts` | `Subscriptions` | getSubscriptions, manageSubscription |
| `bannerSlice.ts` | `Banners` | getBanners, addBanner, deleteBanner |
| `customerSlice.ts` | `Customers` | getCustomers, getCustomerById |
| `discountSlice.ts` | `Discounts` | getDiscounts, addDiscount |
| `notificationSlice.ts` | `Notifications` | getNotifications |
| `metricsSlice.ts` | `Metrics` | getDashboardMetrics |
| `uploadSlice.ts` | — | uploadFile (S3/storage) |

