## 6. Routing Architecture — `src/routes/`

### Route Groups (Role-Based)

| Export | Role | Pages |
|---|---|---|
| `allAdminRoutes` | `admin` | Dashboard, Merchant, Organization, Customer, Reports, Settings |
| `allManagerRoutes` | `manager` | MerchantDashboard, UserManagement, BranchManagement, Profile |
| `allCashierRoutes` | `cashier` | DiscountManagement, Profile |
| `authRoutes` | guest | Login |
| `allSelectBranchRoutes` | guest | BranchSelect |
| `allPublicRoutes` | guest | ForgotPassword, ResetPassword |

### Route Interface
```ts
interface IRoute {
  path: string;
  element: React.ReactNode;
  name: string;
  children?: IRoute[];
  role?: string[] | "admin" | "user" | "guest" | "all";
}
```

### Example: Admin Route with Children
```ts
{
  path: "/merchant",
  element: <MerchantManagement />,
  role: ["admin"],
  children: [
    { path: "/merchant/add",      element: <AddNewMerchant type="add" /> },
    { path: "/merchant/:id",      element: <AddNewMerchant type="view" /> },
    { path: "/merchant/edit/:id", element: <AddNewMerchant type="edit" /> },
  ]
}
```

