## 8. Data Flow Diagram

```
User Action
    │
    ▼
React Component
    │
    ├──► dispatch(action)        → Feature Slice (authSlice / metaSlice)
    │         │                         │
    │         └──────────────────► Redux Store State
    │
    └──► useGetXxxQuery() /     → RTK Query (service slice)
         useMutateXxxMutation()       │
                                      ▼
                               apiSlice (baseQueryWithReauth)
                                      │
                                      ├─► API Server (VITE_API_URL)
                                      │
                                      └─► 401? → Token Refresh → Retry
```

---

## 9. Quick Reference: Common Patterns

### Reading State from Redux
```tsx
import { useSelector } from "react-redux";
import type { RootState } from "@/app/store";

const userInfo = useSelector((state: RootState) => state.auth.userInfo);
const sidebarOpen = useSelector((state: RootState) => state.meta.leftSidebarOpen);
```

### Calling an API (RTK Query)
```tsx
// Query (GET)
const { data, isLoading, error } = useGetMerchantsQuery();

// Mutation (POST/PUT/DELETE)
const [addMerchant, { isLoading }] = useAddMerchantMutation();
await addMerchant({ name: "New Merchant" }).unwrap();
```

### Dispatching an Action
```tsx
import { useDispatch } from "react-redux";
import type { AppDispatch } from "@/app/store";

const dispatch = useDispatch<AppDispatch>();
dispatch(setLeftSidebarOpen(false));
dispatch(logout());
```
